data.description: Welcome to Turnbury Oaks! This gorgeous townhome is located within walking distance to Olde Point Golf Course and just a few minute drive to the local grocery stores and shops. As you enter the property, you are welcomed by the high ceilings and LVP flooring in the main living area and guest bathroom. The first bedroom includes a closet with plenty of natural light on a sunny day. The guest bathroom offers a good amount of cabinet and counter space with a shower/tub combination. The office/study space has been converted to a bedroom and includes a skylight. The closet was added on in the summer of 2023. As you continue through the home you will be guided into the open concept living/dining area. The kitchen overlooks the living room and has the perfect amount of countertop and storage space with a dishwasher that was replaced in 2019. The stove/oven, microwave, and refrigerator have been changed out for stainless steel appliances. Just off the kitchen is the washer and dryer plus a pantry. The living room features lots of natural light and a cozy, welcoming environment with direct access to the back patio. The backyard is fenced in for some privacy and the back door and frame were replaced in 2021. The master bedroom includes a walk in master closet and the master bathroom features a walk in shower. This perfectly sized,  quiet townhome is ready for new owners! Schedule your private tour today!
